These are the weddings you 'll never read about in the untarnished world of bridal magazines : weddings in which a jealous ex-lover sets fire to the newlyweds ' limousine , the bride 's embittered divorced parents ignite a brawl , the couple 's dog relieves himself accompanying them down the aisle , the bride is mugged in the ladies ' room ...
